<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=5.0">
    <title>Instituto IDEM - Desenvolvimento, Equidade e Mudança</title>
    
    <!-- Fontes modernas -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:opsz,wght@14..32,300;14..32,400;14..32,500;14..32,600;14..32,700;14..32,800&family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;0,800;0,900;1,400;1,500;1,600;1,700;1,800;1,900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <!-- Ícones -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        :root {
            --primary-color: #1e3a8a;      /* Azul escuro principal */
            --primary-dark: #1e3a8a;       /* Azul mais escuro */
            --primary-light: #3b82f6;       /* Azul médio */
            --secondary-color: #f97316;     /* Laranja para destaque */
            --secondary-dark: #ea580c;
            --accent-blue: #60a5fa;         /* Azul claro */
            --text-dark: #1e293b;
            --text-gray: #334155;
            --text-light: #64748b;
            --bg-light: #f0f9ff;             /* Fundo azul bem claro */
            --white: #ffffff;
            --shadow-sm: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            --shadow-md: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            --shadow-lg: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            --border-radius: 20px;
            --transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            color: var(--text-dark);
            line-height: 1.5;
            background-color: var(--bg-light);
        }

        /* NAVBAR */
        .navbar {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            width: 100%;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.98);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
            z-index: 1000;
            padding: 1rem 0;
        }

        .nav-container {
            max-width: 1280px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 2rem;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .logo h1 {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }

        .logo p {
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            color: var(--text-light);
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            margin-top: -5px;
        }

        .nav-menu {
            display: flex;
            list-style: none;
            gap: 2rem;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .nav-menu a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: var(--text-gray);
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }

        .nav-menu a:hover {
            color: var(--primary-color);
        }

        .btn-doador-nav {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--secondary-color), var(--secondary-dark));
            color: var(--white) !important;
            padding: 0.6rem 1.5rem !important;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }

        .btn-doador-nav:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.3);
        }

        .btn-padrinho-nav {
            background: transparent;
            border: 2px solid var(--primary-color);
            color: var(--primary-color) !important;
            padding: 0.6rem 1.5rem !important;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .btn-padrinho-nav:hover {
            background: var(--primary-color);
            color: var(--white) !important;
        }

        .hamburger {
            display: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: var(--text-dark);
        }

        /* HERO SECTION */
        .hero {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #eff6ff 0%, #dbeafe 100%);
            padding: 8rem 2rem 4rem;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .hero-container {
            max-width: 1280px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 4rem;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .hero-content h1 {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            line-height: 1.2;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: var(--text-dark);
        }

        .hero-content h1 span {
            color: var(--secondary-color);
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .slogan {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-style: italic;
            border-left: 4px solid var(--secondary-color);
            padding-left: 1rem;
        }

        .hero-content p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: var(--text-light);
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .hero-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--secondary-color), var(--secondary-dark));
            color: var(--white);
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: var(--transition);
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.3);
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            background: transparent;
            border: 2px solid var(--primary-color);
            color: var(--primary-color);
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }

        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background: var(--primary-color);
            color: var(--white);
        }

        .hero-image img {
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: var(--border-radius);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
        }

        /* IMPACTOS SECTION */
        .impactos {
            padding: 4rem 2rem;
            background: var(--white);
        }

        .impactos-container {
            max-width: 1280px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .impactos-header {
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }

        .impactos-header .tag {
            color: var(--secondary-color);
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .impactos-header h2 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .impactos-header h3 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .impactos-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-top: 3rem;
        }

        .impacto-card {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0f9ff, #ffffff);
            border-radius: var(--border-radius);
            transition: var(--transition);
            border: 1px solid rgba(30, 58, 138, 0.1);
        }

        .impacto-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
            border-color: var(--primary-light);
        }

        .impacto-card .number {
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--secondary-color);
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .impacto-card .label {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: var(--text-gray);
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        /* CTA SECTION */
        .cta-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-dark), var(--primary-light));
            padding: 5rem 2rem;
            color: var(--white);
            text-align: center;
        }

        .cta-container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .cta-section h2 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .cta-section p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .cta-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .btn-cta-primary {
            background: var(--secondary-color);
            color: var(--white);
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }

        .btn-cta-primary:hover {
            background: var(--secondary-dark);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .btn-cta-secondary {
            background: transparent;
            border: 2px solid var(--white);
            color: var(--white);
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }

        .btn-cta-secondary:hover {
            background: var(--white);
            color: var(--primary-color);
        }

        /* PROJETOS INCENTIVADOS */
        .projetos-incentivados {
            padding: 5rem 2rem;
            background: var(--bg-light);
        }

        .section-header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }

        .section-header .tag {
            color: var(--secondary-color);
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .section-header h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 800;
        }

        .incentivados-grid {
            max-width: 1280px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        .incentivado-card {
            background: var(--white);
            border-radius: var(--border-radius);
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
            transition: var(--transition);
        }

        .incentivado-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
        }

        .incentivado-card img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 200px;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        .incentivado-content {
            padding: 1.5rem;
        }

        .incentivado-content h3 {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            color: var(--text-dark);
        }

        .incentivado-content p {
            color: var(--text-light);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .incentivado-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 0.3rem 1rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--secondary-color), var(--secondary-dark));
            color: var(--white);
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        /* NOTÍCIAS */
        .noticias {
            padding: 5rem 2rem;
            background: var(--white);
        }

        .noticias-grid {
            max-width: 1280px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        .noticia-card {
            background: var(--white);
            border-radius: var(--border-radius);
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
            transition: var(--transition);
            border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }

        .noticia-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
        }

        .noticia-card img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 200px;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        .noticia-content {
            padding: 1.5rem;
        }

        .noticia-date {
            color: var(--secondary-color);
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .noticia-content h3 {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            color: var(--text-dark);
        }

        .noticia-content p {
            color: var(--text-light);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .read-more {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }

        .read-more:hover {
            gap: 0.8rem;
        }

        /* DENÚNCIA */
        .denuncia-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e293b, #0f172a);
            padding: 4rem 2rem;
            color: var(--white);
        }

        .denuncia-container {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .denuncia-container i {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: var(--secondary-color);
        }

        .denuncia-container h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .denuncia-container p {
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .btn-denuncia {
            background: var(--secondary-color);
            color: var(--white);
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }

        .btn-denuncia:hover {
            background: var(--secondary-dark);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        /* FOOTER */
        .footer {
            background: var(--text-dark);
            color: var(--white);
            padding: 4rem 2rem 2rem;
        }

        .footer-container {
            max-width: 1280px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 3rem;
        }

        .footer-section h4 {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: var(--secondary-color);
        }

        .footer-section p, .footer-section a {
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
            text-decoration: none;
            line-height: 2;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }

        .footer-section a:hover {
            color: var(--secondary-color);
        }

        .social-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }

        .social-links a {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }

        .copyright {
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 3rem;
            margin-top: 3rem;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
        }

        /* MODAL DOAÇÃO */
        .modal {
            display: none;
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.8);
            z-index: 2000;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .modal-content {
            background: var(--white);
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: var(--border-radius);
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 90%;
            position: relative;
        }

        .modal-close {
            position: absolute;
            top: 1rem;
            right: 1rem;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .pix-info {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color), var(--primary-light));
            color: var(--white);
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border-radius: var(--border-radius);
            text-align: center;
            margin: 1.5rem 0;
        }

        .pix-copy {
            background: var(--white);
            color: var(--primary-color);
            border: none;
            padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }

        /* RESPONSIVE */
        @media (max-width: 968px) {
            .hero-container {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                text-align: center;
            }

            .hero-buttons {
                justify-content: center;
            }

            .impactos-grid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            }

            .slogan {
                text-align: left;
            }

            .hamburger {
                display: block;
            }

            .nav-menu {
                position: fixed;
                left: -100%;
                top: 70px;
                flex-direction: column;
                background: var(--white);
                width: 100%;
                padding: 2rem;
                box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
                transition: 0.3s;
                gap: 1.5rem;
            }

            .nav-menu.active {
                left: 0;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 640px) {
            .impactos-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .hero-content h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }

            .slogan {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }

            .cta-buttons {
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            .hero-buttons {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- NAVBAR -->
    <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="nav-container">
            <div class="logo">
                <h1>IDEM</h1>
                <p>Instituto de Desenvolvimento, Equidade e Mudança</p>
            </div>
            <div class="hamburger">
                <i class="fas fa-bars"></i>
            </div>
            <ul class="nav-menu">
                <li><a href="#home">INÍCIO</a></li>
                <li><a href="#" id="btnPadrinhoNav" class="btn-padrinho-nav">SEJA UM PADRINHO</a></li>
                <li><a href="#historia">NOSSA HISTÓRIA</a></li>
                <li><a href="#projetos-incentivados">PROJETOS INCENTIVADOS</a></li>
                <li><a href="#projetos">PROJETOS</a></li>
                <li><a href="#" id="btnTransparenciaNav">TRANSPARÊNCIA</a></li>
                <li><a href="#noticias">NOTÍCIAS</a></li>
                <li><a href="#denuncia">DENÚNCIA</a></li>
                <li><a href="#" class="btn-doador-nav" id="btnDoadorNav">DOE AGORA</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- MODAL DOAÇÃO -->
    <div id="modalDoacao" class="modal">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <span class="modal-close">&times;</span>
            <h2 style="color: var(--primary-color); text-align: center;">Faça sua Doação</h2>
            <div class="pix-info">
                <p><i class="fas fa-qrcode"></i> Doe via PIX</p>
                <strong>41.572.637/0001-30</strong>
                <br>
                <button class="pix-copy" onclick="copiarPix()">Copiar chave PIX</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- HERO SECTION -->
    <section id="home" class="hero">
        <div class="hero-container">
            <div class="hero-content">
                <h1>Transformando vidas através da <span>equidade e mudança social</span></h1>
                <div class="slogan">
                    "Semeando oportunidades, colhendo futuros"
                </div>
                <p>Construindo pontes para um futuro mais justo e igualitário através de projetos sociais, educacionais e culturais que transformam realidades.</p>
                <div class="hero-buttons">
                    <a href="#" class="btn-primary" id="btnDoadorHero"><i class="fas fa-hand-holding-heart"></i> FAÇA SUA INSCRIÇÃO</a>
                    <a href="#" class="btn-primary" id="btnDoadorHero2"><i class="fas fa-heart"></i> DOE AGORA</a>
                    <a href="#" class="btn-secondary" id="btnPadrinhoHero">SEJA UM PADRINHO</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="hero-image">
                <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/institucionalosc/institucionalofical/refs/heads/main/Estruturas%20para%20site%20(1).png" alt="Instituto IDEM">
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- IMPACTOS SECTION -->
    <section class="impactos">
        <div class="impactos-container">
            <div class="impactos-header">
                <div class="tag">NOSSOS IMPACTOS EM 2025</div>
                <h2>#TransformandoVidas</h2>
                <h3>Resultados que inspiram mudanças reais</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="impactos-grid">
                <div class="impacto-card">
                    <div class="number">+500</div>
                    <div class="label">Pessoas atendidas</div>
                </div>
                <div class="impacto-card">
                    <div class="number">+200</div>
                    <div class="label">TONELADAS</div>
                </div>
                <div class="impacto-card">
                    <div class="number">+18.000</div>
                    <div class="label">Atendimentos realizados</div>
                </div>
                <div class="impacto-card">
                    <div class="number">R$ 750.000</div>
                    <div class="label">Recursos captados</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA SECTION -->
    <section class="cta-section">
        <div class="cta-container">
            <h2>Seja um Padrinho do IDEM</h2>
            <p>Com apenas R$ 30 por mês, você transforma a vida de uma criança e contribui para um futuro de oportunidades.</p>
            <div class="cta-buttons">
                <a href="#" class="btn-cta-primary" id="btnPadrinhoCta">QUERO SER PADRINHO</a>
                <a href="#" class="btn-cta-secondary" id="btnDoadorCta">FAZER DOAÇÃO ÚNICA</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- PROJETOS INCENTIVADOS -->
    <section id="projetos-incentivados" class="projetos-incentivados">
        <div class="section-header">
            <div class="tag">PROJETOS INCENTIVADOS</div>
            <h2>Conheça nossos projetos com incentivo fiscal</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="incentivados-grid">
            <div class="incentivado-card">
                <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/400x200?text=Curso+de+Manicure" alt="Curso de Manicure">
                <div class="incentivado-content">
                    <h3>Curso de Manicure</h3>
                    <p>Capacitação profissional gratuita para mulheres em vulnerabilidade social.</p>
                    <span class="incentivado-badge">Lei de Incentivo</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="incentivado-card">
                <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/400x200?text=Inclusão+Social" alt="Inclusão Social">
                <div class="incentivado-content">
                    <h3>Inclusão Social</h3>
                    <p>Programa de integração social com rodas de conversa e desenvolvimento pessoal.</p>
                    <span class="incentivado-badge">Lei Rouanet</span>
